<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ekstrakurikuler - SMPN SATU ATAP TUBAKI</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">

    <style>
        /* Hero Header */
        .hero-ekskul {
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.7), rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.7)), 
                              url('/gambar/bg-ekskul.jpg'); 
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 350px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .hero-ekskul h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        /* Section Konten */
        .ekskul-section {
            padding: 80px 10%;
            background-color: #fffaf5;
        }

        .ekskul-intro {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px;
        }

        .ekskul-intro h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Grid Ekstrakurikuler */
        .ekskul-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .ekskul-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: 0.3s;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #003366;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .ekskul-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .ekskul-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .ekskul-info {
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .ekskul-info i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #b8860b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .ekskul-info h3 {
            color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        }

        .ekskul-info p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .jadwal-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #003366;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="top-header">
        <div class="logo-wrapper">
            <img src="/gambar/logo1.png" alt="Logo" style="height: 50px; margin-right: 10px;">
            <div style="line-height: 1;">
                <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #666;">Website Resmi</span><br>
                <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #003366;">SMPN SATU ATAP TUBAKI</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li><a href="/">üè† HOME</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">PROFIL ‚ñº</a>
                    <ul class="submenu">
                        <li><a href="/guru">Guru dan Staf</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/tentang-sekolah">Tentang Sekolah</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/visimisi">Visi & Misi</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><a href="#">AKADEMIK ‚ñº</a>
                    <ul class="submenu">
                        <li><a href="/kurikulum">Kurikulum</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/prestasi">Prestasi</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><a href="#">KESISWAAN ‚ñº</a>
                    <ul class="submenu">
                        <li><a href="/osis">OSIS</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/ekstrakurikuler">Ekstrakurikuler</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><a href="/berita">BERITA</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">GALERI ‚ñº</a>
                    <ul class="submenu">
                        <li><a href="/galeri">Foto Kegiatan</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/video">Video Dokumentasi</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><a href="#">PPDB ‚ñº</a>
                    <ul class="submenu">
                        <li><a href="/persyaratan">Persyaratan</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/formulir">Formulir Pendaftaran</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><a href="/kontak">KONTAK</a></li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/login" class="btn-login">üë§ LOGIN</a>
        </div>
    </nav>


    <header class="hero-ekskul">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Ekstrakurikuler</h1>
            <p>Mengembangkan Bakat, Minat, dan Kreativitas Siswa</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="ekskul-section">
        <div class="ekskul-intro">
            <h2>Pilihan Kegiatan Bakat & Minat</h2>
            <p>Kami menyediakan berbagai wadah bagi siswa untuk mengeksplorasi potensi diri di luar jam pelajaran akademik.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ekskul-grid">
            <%# CEK APAKAH VARIABEL daftarEkskul ADA DAN TIDAK KOSONG %>
            <% if (typeof daftarEkskul !== 'undefined' && daftarEkskul.length > 0) { %>
                <% daftarEkskul.forEach(ekskul => { %>
                    <div class="ekskul-card">
                        <%# PERBAIKAN: Menggunakan folder /gambar/ jika itu lokasi penyimpanan upload Anda %>
                        <img src="/gambar/<%= ekskul.gambar %>" alt="<%= ekskul.nama %>" class="ekskul-img" onerror="this.src='/gambar/default-ekskul.jpg'">
                        <div class="ekskul-info">
                            <%# Ikon default piala jika di DB kosong %>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-trophy"></i>
                            <h3><%= ekskul.nama %></h3>
                            <p><%= ekskul.deskripsi %></p>
                            <%# Tampilkan badge hanya jika kolom jadwal ada di DB (Opsional) %>
                            <% if(ekskul.jadwal) { %>
                                <span class="jadwal-badge"><%= ekskul.jadwal %></span>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <%# TAMPILAN JIKA TIDAK ADA DATA DI DATABASE %>
                <div class="ekskul-grid" style="grid-column: 1/-1; text-align: center;">
                    <p>Belum ada data kegiatan ekstrakurikuler yang ditambahkan.</p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 60px;">
            <a href="/" style="background: #003366; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.3s; display: inline-block;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Kembali ke Home
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="main-footer" style="background-color: #1a3a5f; color: white; padding: 40px 10% 20px;">
        <div class="footer-bottom" style="text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 20px;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.6;">&copy; 2026 SMPN Satu Atap Tubaki. Hak Cipta Dilindungi.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>